This is the software, for the Infinity_mirror Part 1, published 
in The MagPi No. 43 March 2016

distance.py - tests the distance sensor.
mirror1.py - is the full code for the project so far

Images - contains some extra photos of the project

A video of this project can be seen at:-
https://vimeo.com/156278316

Note next month's project will add an unconventional OLED time display, it might surprise you.